{"tid":777821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"估地方！暑假初嚐禁果　18歲少女屌到子宮頸潰爛","createTime":"2018-08-13T08:18:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-13T08:41:08.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5f9b7fcc8b01d88363c446a7ba252f89b0081c09","tid":777821,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T08:18:53.000Z","msg":"一名剛滿18歲的王姓女子，日前與男友在暑假期間初嚐禁果，性行為第二天就出現陰部紅、癢等症狀，但拖了近2周才因為疼痛難耐到醫院就診，醫師發現，子宮頸已出現潰爛狀況，醫生趕緊用抗生素治療，並開出口服藥方，1周後王女狀況好轉，2星期治癒，醫生表示，可能是未注意私密處清潔，加上另一半也未注意清潔，容易細菌感染引發紅腫、潰爛。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20180813/1409988\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20180813%2F1409988&d=wpE2yiyToc0kp6Chx5CYKcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=9fe11f4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20180813%2F1409988&h=66521652\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20180813/1409988</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c69f3e60f6f1613474a1752b409d6c77b86c43","tid":777821,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T08:20:12.000Z","msg":"以為係新北<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88cf5dfb6c8f39de72869a1b188e76b94dafbb58","tid":777821,"uid":39381,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T08:20:19.000Z","msg":"頂到子宮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a45a3129d858ffab314a7c1235898def8dc4de5","tid":777821,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T08:21:25.000Z","msg":"點樣屌可以屌到咁<br />\n真係對穿牆? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"677cf9769c917dbecb73ec9afe5edf7423603333","tid":777821,"uid":11067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited